The paper discusses the conflicts between GDPR regulations and the design, architecture, and operation of modern systems, which are related to cybersecurity (cs.CR), cyber law and policy (cs.CY), software engineering (cs.SE), databases (cs.DB), and machine learning (cs.LG) as modern systems often involve data processing and analysis.
